/**Here are some files that may help you a bit with your Arduino ATmega328.
*
*Scalextric cars and tracks are fun, what could be better than combine it with the fun of Arduino?
*Schematic in Fritzing format is currently for one input and output.
*Use at your own risk and race !

*Potentiometers in scalextric controllers need little mod-hacking (currently in off-state will bring the input to non-stable input), photos will be added here.


